ZH: 我的电脑需要定期杀毒。
EN: My computer needs to be regularly scanned for viruses.

ZH: 他购买了一个好的杀毒软件。
EN: He purchased a good antivirus software.

ZH: 为了保护数据安全，请务必及时更新杀毒软件。
EN: To protect data security, please remember to update the antivirus software in time.

ZH: 他的手机被病毒感染了，需要进行杀毒处理。
EN: His phone has been infected by a virus and needs antivirus treatment.

ZH: 这个杀毒程序可以有效防止病毒入侵。
EN: This antivirus program can effectively prevent virus attacks.

ZH: 每天对电脑进行一次全面杀毒是必要的。
EN: It is necessary to run a full scan on the computer for viruses every day.

ZH: 请不要关闭杀毒软件，以免系统受到病毒攻击。
EN: Please do not turn off the antivirus software to avoid virus attacks on the system.

ZH: 使用不明来源的存储设备可能导致电脑感染病毒，一定要及时进行杀毒检查。
EN: Using storage devices from unknown sources may lead to computer virus infection, be sure to conduct antivirus checks in a timely manner.

ZH: 为了避免病毒传播，请下载安全可靠的杀毒软件。
EN: To prevent virus transmission, download secure and reliable antivirus software.

ZH: 杀毒软件可以及时提醒您有病毒威胁。
EN: Antivirus software can notify you of virus threats in a timely manner.

ZH: 他们正在开发更高效的杀毒技术。
EN: They are developing more efficient antivirus technologies.

ZH: 我们公司每周都会对所有电脑进行杀毒检查。
EN: Our company conducts antivirus checks on all computers every week.

ZH: 在线购物时最好使用杀毒软件保护账户信息。
EN: It is best to use antivirus software when shopping online to protect account information.

ZH: 经常清理电脑垃圾文件有助于杀毒效果。
EN: Regularly cleaning up computer junk files helps with antivirus effectiveness.

ZH: 请在下载软件前检查文件安全性并运行杀毒程序。
EN: Please check the security of files before downloading software and run antivirus programs.

ZH: 确保手机上装有可靠的杀毒软件以防止恶意软件攻击。
EN: Make sure your phone has reliable antivirus software to prevent malicious software attacks.

ZH: 这个杀毒软件有强大的病毒防治能力。
EN: This antivirus software has powerful virus prevention capabilities.

ZH: 记得定期更新你的杀毒软件以保持最新的病毒库。
EN: Remember to regularly update your antivirus software to keep the virus database up to date.

ZH: 换个杀毒软件试试，也许效果会更好。
EN: Try a different antivirus software, it might work better.

ZH: 杀毒是保护电脑安全的重要步骤。
EN: Antivirus is an important step in protecting computer security. 

(Note: 杀毒 means antivirus/antivirus software in Chinese)
